dc_description_s: This point shapefile shows locations of market centers in western Kenya. This data was used in Map 3.15 in Nature's Benefits in Kenya: An Atlas of Ecosystems and Human Well-Being. Geological Survey of Kenya and International Livestock Research Institute. (2000). Market Centers in Western Kenya, 2000. Geological Survey of Kenya. Available at: http://purl.stanford.edu/sb710sh4558 Data set is not for use in litigation.
